OL,3,CThe price of an underpoured pint:
OL,4,CShort measures cost drinkers #115 a
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FCustomers have a right to ask for
OL,8,Ftheir drinks to be topped up if they
OL,9,Fdon't think they've been given what
OL,10,Fthey paid for, but increasingly this
OL,11,Fis not happening, ITV News
OL,12,FCorrespondent Kelly Foran reports
OL,14,FPub-goers hoping for a pint this
OL,15,Fweekend might be left shortchanged -
OL,16,Fafter an investigation found two-
OL,17,Fthirds of beer and wine orders were
OL,18,Funder-poured.
