OL,3,CThe price of an underpoured pint:
OL,4,CShort measures cost drinkers #115 a
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FTrading Standards Officers visited 77
OL,8,Fpubs and bars, and found they were
OL,9,Fserved 96 short measures out of 137
OL,10,Forders.
OL,12,FThat means around 70% of drinks were
OL,13,Fless than the prescribed quantity
OL,14,Frequired by the Weights and Measures
OL,15,FOrder for pints, half pints, and 175ml
OL,16,Fglasses of wine.
OL,18,FSome 86% of all beer ordered was short
OL,19,Fmeasured, as was 43% of wine.
