OL,7,FAnd that shortfall adds up. CTSI Chief
OL,8,FExecutive, John Herriman, said there
OL,9,Fwas a "potential detriment to the
OL,10,Faverage consumer of around #115 every
OL,11,Fyear."
OL,13,FThe Chartered Trading Services
OL,14,FInstitute (CTSI) estimates for the
OL,15,Faverage , short measuring equates to a
OL,16,Floss of #1.70 a week - or #88.40 a
OL,17,Fyear.
OL,19,FFor the that amount jumps to #2.20 a
OL,20,Fweek - or #114.40 a year.
