OL,7,FThe largest short measure researchers
OL,8,Ffound was 15% under, on a #3.20 glass
OL,9,Fof wine in Walsall. In Belfast, a
OL,10,F#7.20 glass of wine was found to be
OL,11,F13.4% under poured.
OL,13,FThe average deficit for short-measured
OL,14,Fbeer was 4%, while for wine it was 5%.
