OL,3,CThe price of an underpoured pint:
OL,4,CShort measures cost drinkers #115 a
OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FThe average price of a bottle of red
OL,8,Fwine has increased by 8% in the last
OL,9,Fyear, while the average cost of a pint
OL,10,Fof lager is up 5.6%, according to the
OL,11,FOffice for National Statistics.
OL,13,FCTSI Chief Executive, John Herriman,
OL,14,Fsaid the findings paint "a national
OL,15,Fpicture of how widespread short
OL,16,Fmeasuring of alcoholic drinks are."
OL,18,FHe called on the hospitality sector to
OL,19,Fensure consumers were being served
OL,20,Fdrinks that were correctly measured.
