OL,5,Cyear
OL,7,FLegally, the frothy head on a pint of
OL,8,Fbeer is included in the measure, but
OL,9,Fthe CTSI found that only 23% of the
OL,10,Fpublic think that should be the case.
OL,12,F(CAMRA) maintains the pint measure
OL,13,Fshould not include the head and
OL,14,Fconsumers should have a right to a
OL,15,F100% liquid pint.
OL,17,FCAMRA national chairman Nik Anton said
OL,18,Fthe CTSI's findings were "concerning".
OL,19,FHe urged consumers served anything
OL,20,Fmore than 5% short to "ask bar staff
OL,21,Ffor an immediate top-up."
